LINE.Text: Here are some of the protocols that
have been put in place to protect those
traveling to Saint Lucia and Her citizens
THROUGHOUT YOUR STAY IN SAINT LUCIA
Departure lounge rearranged to allow for social distancing
Passport bio-page and departing flight details on hand
Only departing guests will be allowed into terminal building
Complete and submit your Pre-Arrival Registration Form
COVID 19 certified taxis only booked by hotel
(PPE, Sanitation and Social Distancing cashless transaction protocols in place]
Take a PCR test no more than 7 days before travel
and receive confirmation of a negative PCR test result.
Limited contact check in and check out
Temperature checks for guests at mealtimes
Don't forget to wear your mask
Follow the directions of the ground staff and signage
Guests are required to remain at their hotel for the
duration of their stay. Please consult with your hotel
